{"categories":[{"name":"Movies","videos":[{"id":"big-buck-bunny","title":"Big Buck Bunny","subtitle":"Blender Foundation","description":"A giant rabbit with a heart bigger than himself takes comical revenge on three rude rodents. Classic open-source animation from the Blender Foundation.","type":"youtube","sources":["https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YE7VzlLtp-4"],"thumb":"/images/thumbs/big-buck-bunny.jpg","youtubeId":"YE7VzlLtp-4"},{"id":"sintel","title":"Sintel","subtitle":"Blender Foundation","description":"An independently produced short fantasy film by the Blender Foundation, following a girl searching for her lost dragon companion.","type":"youtube","sources":["https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eRsGyueVLvQ"],"thumb":"/images/thumbs/sintel.jpg","youtubeId":"eRsGyueVLvQ"},{"id":"tears-of-steel","title":"Tears of Steel","subtitle":"Blender Foundation","description":"A compelling sci-fi short film realized with crowd-funding, testing a complete open and free pipeline for visual effects.","type":"youtube","sources":["https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R6MlUcmOul8"],"thumb":"/images/thumbs/tears-of-steel.jpg","youtubeId":"R6MlUcmOul8"},{"id":"elephants-dream","title":"Elephants Dream","subtitle":"Blender Foundation","description":"The first Blender Open Movie from 2006 — a surreal journey through a strange machine world.","type":"youtube","sources":["https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TLkA0RELQ1g"],"thumb":"/images/thumbs/elephants-dream.jpg","youtubeId":"TLkA0RELQ1g"},{"id":"me-at-the-zoo","title":"Me at the zoo","subtitle":"jawed","description":"The first video ever uploaded to YouTube, recorded at the San Diego Zoo in 2005.","type":"youtube","sources":["https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jNQXAC9IVRw"],"thumb":"/images/thumbs/me-at-the-zoo.jpg","youtubeId":"jNQXAC9IVRw"},{"id":"keyboard-cat","title":"Keyboard Cat","subtitle":"Keyboard Cat","description":"The iconic viral video of a cat playing keyboard — one of the earliest internet memes.","type":"youtube","sources":["https: